### Register
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Shopkeeper User",
  "email": "shopkeeper@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "shopkeeper"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "shopkeeper@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Verify Email
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/auth/verify-email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "shopkeeper@example.com",
  "token": "paste_token_from_mail_log"
}

### Forgot Password
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "shopkeeper@example.com"
}

### Update Consumer Profile
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/v1/profile/me
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "John Doe",
  "deliveryContacts": [
    { "recipientName": "John Doe", "address": "Home: 12 Main Street" },
    { "recipientName": "Jane Doe", "address": "Office: 45 Market Road" }
  ],
  "mobileNumber": "9876543210",
  "alternateNumber": "9123456780"
}

### Create Order
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "shippingDetails": {
    "recipientName": "John Doe",
    "address": "12 Main Street, NY",
    "mobileNumber": "9876543210",
    "alternateNumber": "9123456780"
  }
}

### Cancel Order
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/v1/orders/:orderId/cancel
